high_descs: turn right and walk forwards past the chair on your left, but then turn left and walk over to the front of the coffee table which will be on your right up ahead
grab the remote controller off of the coffee table there
turn right and walk over to the chair you passed earlier which is now on your right just up ahead
place the remote controller down on top of the chair there
turn right and walk over to the front of the coffee table again up ahead on your right, turn to face it too
grab the second remote controller off of the coffee table
turn right and walk over to the chair up ahead on your right where you put the other remote controller down on top of
place the remote controller down on top of the chair there again
anns.task_desc: place two remote controller's down on top of the chair in the living room

high_descs: Turn around and take a step forward, then turn left and walk over to the coffee table.
Pick up the rightmost remote off of the coffee table.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn right to face the chair with the book on its seat.
Put the remote on the left side of the seat of the chair.
Turn right and walk towards the fireplace, then turn right to face the coffee table.
Pick up the remote off of the coffee table.
Turn right and walk towards the wall, then turn right to face the chair.
Put the remote on the chair behind the remote that is already there.
anns.task_desc: Move two remotes to the seat of a chair.

high_descs: Turn around and walk around the couch to the coffee table.
Pick up the right remote off of the coffee table.
Turn to the right and face the single seat couch.
Put the remote on the seat of the couch.
Turn to the right and move to the coffee table.
Pick up the remote off of the coffee table.
Turn to the right and face the single seat couch.
Put the remote above the other remote on the seat of the couch.
anns.task_desc: Organize the remotes onto the single seat couch.
